kpi_info.title: NUMBER OF THREE SCHEDULED HSDPA USER PER TTI
kpi_info.use: Number of three simultaneously scheduled HSDPA users per TTI in WCELL. UPDATED: Incremented for every TTI for which there is data in the HSDPA user buffers and the data (MAC-hs PDU) is scheduled to be sent to the three user.
